Functional properties of 
   RSP recovered from different 
   EAE treatments. (A) Protein solubility; (B) Emulsifying property; (C) Foaming property. Bars with different letters in the same group indicate statistical difference (
   p < 0.05, Duncan's test). 
   EAE, enzyme‐assisted aqueous extraction; 
   EAI, emulsifying activity index; 
   ESI, emulsifying stability index; 
   FC, foaming capacity; 
   FS, foaming stability; 
   RSP, recovered skim protein
